k10_me_2_rate_3_11_7_13.title: High or Very High Psychological Distress Levels (K-10) - Rate per 100
k10_me_2_rate_3_11_7_13.description: Estimated number of people aged 18 years and over with high or very high psychological distress as a rate per 100 people - modelled estimate. Source: Compiled by PHIDU using predictions from the 2011-13 Australian Health Survey, ABS (unpublished) and ABS Estimated Resident Population, average of 30 June 2011 and 2012.
